name: Cat contemplating a solitary avenue
description: I was walking by one the loneliest avenues in the small town where I live, and I saw this mysterious black cat peacefully contemplating the empty avenue, luckily I was carrying my DSLR so I took this shot. This picture was taken on April 26, 2021, at the General Vásquez avenue of La Esperanza, Intibucá, Honduras, C.A.
